title: Tana Con is coming back?! Here we go
description:
Manny and Laura are back for another episode of Fool Coverage and this week is rapid fire! They cover rumors of a potential TanaCon 2, the spilled tea amongst the cast of the film "Don't Worry Darling," Britney Spears slamming her son in a voice note, Yung Gravy and Sheri Nicole's PDA at the VMAS, why we should all stop riding the rides at carnivals, and more!

Follow Laura on IG: @larlarlee
Follow Manny on IG: @mannymua733
